OL,3,CFormer Preston manager David Moyes
OL,4,Cunveils train dedicated to club
OL,6,FFormer Preston North End manager David
OL,7,FMoyes has unveiled a commemorative
OL,8,Ftrain - named after the club.
OL,10,FMoyes unveiled the nameplate at an
OL,11,Fevent at Preston Railway Station on 31
OL,12,FMarch, hung on the side of a GB
OL,13,FRailfreight locomotive.
OL,15,FHe said: "It's a great thing for
OL,16,FPreston North End, well deserved
OL,17,Fbecause it's an incredibly well known,
OL,18,Ffamous football club, with a one and
OL,19,Fonly North End."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
