OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775056271
OL,3,CFormer Preston manager David Moyes
OL,4,Cunveils train dedicated to club
OL,6,FMoyes became Preston manager in 1998 -
OL,7,Fwhen they were in danger of relegation
OL,8,Ffrom Division Two - his first managing
OL,9,Fjob after making more than 530 league
OL,10,Fappearances in his playing career.
OL,12,FHe paid tribute to Sir Tom Finney - a
OL,13,FPreston legend who made over 400
OL,14,Fappearances for the club, as well as
OL,15,Fwinning 76 England caps in his career.
OL,17,F"When you think of Preston North End
OL,18,Fyou think of Sir Tom Finney, and if he
OL,19,Fwas alive today, it would be Sir Tom
OL,20,Fwho would be down here unveiling
OL,21,Fthis," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
