PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775056271
OL,3,CFormer Preston manager David Moyes
OL,4,Cunveils train dedicated to club
OL,6,FMoyes led the club to the Division Two
OL,7,Ftitle and promotion to Division One
OL,8,Fthe following season, where his team
OL,9,Falso made the playoffs.
OL,11,FHe spent four years with the club
OL,12,Fbefore he joined Everton in 2002. He
OL,13,Fled Preston through 234 matches,
OL,14,Fwinning 113.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
